fields.name: CLINTON AGEBOBA
fields.title: Software Developer & Tech Advocate
fields.bio: Passionate software developer with expertise in full-stack development. I love building innovative solutions and contributing to open-source projects. Always eager to learn new technologies and share knowledge with the developer community.

fields.title: E-Commerce Platform
fields.description: A full-stack e-commerce platform with payment integration
fields.long_description: Built a comprehensive e-commerce solution using React and Django. Features include user authentication, product management, shopping cart, payment processing with Stripe, and order tracking. The platform supports multiple payment methods and includes an admin dashboard for managing products and orders.

fields.title: Task Management App
fields.description: Collaborative task management application with real-time updates
fields.long_description: A modern task management application built with React and Django REST Framework. Features real-time collaboration, drag-and-drop task organization, file attachments, and team workspaces. Includes advanced filtering and search capabilities.

fields.title: Portfolio Website
fields.description: Personal portfolio website showcasing projects and skills
fields.long_description: A responsive portfolio website built with React and styled with modern CSS. Features include project showcase, skills display, contact form, and blog section. Fully responsive design with smooth animations and transitions.

fields.description: Leading development of web applications and mentoring junior developers. Working with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software solutions.
responsibilities: Develop and maintain web applications using React and Django
Mentor junior developers and conduct code reviews
Collaborate with product managers and designers

fields.description: Developed and maintained multiple client projects using modern web technologies. Worked on both frontend and backend development.
responsibilities: Built responsive web applications using React and Vue.js
Developed RESTful APIs using Django and Flask
Collaborated with clients to understand requirements
